OL,3,CWood manufacturer fined #160,000 after
OL,4,Cworker lost leg in 'preventable'
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FA large wood manufacturer has been
OL,8,Ffined #160,000 after an employee
OL,9,Fsustained life-changing injuries when
OL,10,Fworking at their Ellesmere premises.
OL,12,FRobert Stubbs, 37, sustained life-
OL,13,Fchanging injuries when clearing a
OL,14,Fjammed log on a machine in May 2021 at
OL,15,FE.T.C. Sawmills Limited.
OL,17,FHe climbed onto a stationary conveyor
OL,18,Fbed and used a metal pole to move a
OL,19,Flog, but the conveyor started to move
OL,20,Funexpectedly, trapping his leg against
OL,21,Fa stop plate.
