OL,3,CWood manufacturer fined #160,000 after
OL,4,Cworker lost leg in 'preventable'
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FThe 37-year-old had his right leg
OL,8,Famputated below the knee and sustained
OL,9,Fsignificant injuries to his left leg.
OL,11,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,12,FSafety Executive (HSE) found that
OL,13,FE.T.C. Sawmills Limited failed to
OL,14,Fadequately assess the risks and devise
OL,15,Fand implement effective measures to
OL,16,Fprevent access to the dangerous moving
OL,17,Fparts of the Quad Saw machine or to
OL,18,Fstop the movement of the dangerous
OL,19,Fparts before people entered the danger
OL,20,Fzones.
