OL,3,CWood manufacturer fined #160,000 after
OL,4,Cworker lost leg in 'preventable'
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FThe company also failed to provide
OL,8,Femployees with safe systems of work or
OL,9,Fsuitable and sufficient information,
OL,10,Finstruction, training and supervision
OL,11,Fto enable safe operation of the
OL,12,Fmachine.
OL,14,FAlthough standards of health and
OL,15,Fsafety are much improved over recent
OL,16,Fyears, sawmilling remains a high-risk
OL,17,Findustry with a major injury rate that
OL,18,Fis over two and a half times that of
OL,19,Fgeneral manufacturing.
