OL,3,CWood manufacturer fined #160,000 after
OL,4,Cworker lost leg in 'preventable'
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FHSE Inspector Keeley Eves said: "E.T.C
OL,8,FSawmills is one of the largest
OL,9,Fmanufacturers of softwoods for the
OL,10,Ffencing and pallet industries in
OL,11,FEngland.
OL,13,F"The life-changing injuries sustained
OL,14,Fby Mr Stubbs could easily have been
OL,15,Fprevented if the company had acted to
OL,16,Fidentify and manage the risks
OL,17,Finvolved, put a safe system of work in
OL,18,Fplace and ensured that employees were
OL,19,Fappropriately trained and supervised."
